OL,3,C#11m Star of Caledonia project given
OL,4,Cthe green light
OL,6,FProposals to build a multi-million
OL,7,Fpound Star of Caledonia sculpture in
OL,8,FGretna Green have been approved by
OL,9,FDumfries and Galloway Council.
OL,11,FThe #11m giant sculpture, expected to
OL,12,Fbe taller than the Angel of the North
OL,13,Fat 33 metres, has been in the planning
OL,14,Fsince 2001.
OL,16,FThe Star of Caledonia Trust believes
OL,17,Fthe 39-acre site will bring 250,000
OL,18,Fpeople every year to the England-
OL,19,FScotland border. The artwork will be
OL,20,Flocated in a field next to Gretna
OL,21,FGreen.
