OL,3,C#11m Star of Caledonia project given
OL,4,Cthe green light
OL,6,FThe concept, which is hoped to be
OL,7,Fbuilt by 2027, was first created by
OL,8,Ffarmer and business owner Alasdair
OL,9,FHouston 24 years ago. Mr Houston led
OL,10,Fthe project until he died in 2021.
OL,12,FHis wife, Lucy Houston, has since
OL,13,Ftaken on his campaign with the hope of
OL,14,F'transforming his vision into reality.'
